這裡可以讓你自由使用喔。<delay20 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="102_01_02" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣啊？<delay20 />你不用這麼客氣的！<delay frames="60" />
