攝影棚是可以讓你自由使用的。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="102_02" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那麼，<delay8 />我到外面去<delay frames="30" />
呼吸一下新鮮空氣，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你有什麼不懂的地方，<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />再出來問我。</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好的！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />包在我身上！<10_4 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那麼，我要開始說了<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在攝影棚拍照<delay20 />
主要分成三大部分，<delay frames="40" /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><10_4 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />包括了<delay frames="30" />攝影棚的<colour id="1" />場景<colour id="65535" />、<delay frames="30" /><colour id="1" />模特兒<colour id="65535" />以及<delay20 /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><colour id="1" />服裝<colour id="65535" />！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也就是說，<delay frames="30" /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />整個流程主要是這樣<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
首先是配置場景，<delay frames="30" />接著是安排模特兒，<delay frames="40" />
再來是換裝，<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />最後就可以拍照了。</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="08 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><colour id="1" />場景<colour id="65535" />、<delay20 /><colour id="1" />模特兒<colour id="65535" />、<delay20 /><colour id="1" />服裝<colour id="65535" />，<delay frames="40" />
接著是<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />最重要的<colour id="1" />拍照<colour id="65535" />，<delay frames="30" />
關於這些，<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要聽我稍微說明一下嗎？</message>
